Sentencas: YSZ electrolyte coatings were prepared by electron beam physical vapor deposition (EB-PVD) at a high deposition rate of up to 1 mm/min.
Titulo: Electron beam physical vapor deposition of YSZ electrolyte coatings for SOFCs

Sentencas: The YSZ coating consisted of a single cubic phase and no phase transformation occurred after annealing treatment at 1000 degrees C. A typical columnar structure was observed in this coating by SEM and feather-like characteristics appeared in every columnar grain.
Titulo: Electron beam physical vapor deposition of YSZ electrolyte coatings for SOFCs

Sentencas: In columnar grain boundaries there were many micron-sized gaps and pores.
Titulo: Electron beam physical vapor deposition of YSZ electrolyte coatings for SOFCs

Sentencas: In TEM image, many white lines were found, originating from the alignment of nanopores existing within feather-like columnar grains.
Titulo: Electron beam physical vapor deposition of YSZ electrolyte coatings for SOFCs

Sentencas: The element distribution along the cross-section of the coating was homogeneous except Zr with a slight gradient.
Titulo: Electron beam physical vapor deposition of YSZ electrolyte coatings for SOFCs

Sentencas: The coating exhibited a characteristic anisotropic behavior in electrical conductivity.
Titulo: Electron beam physical vapor deposition of YSZ electrolyte coatings for SOFCs

Sentencas: In the direction perpendicular to coating surface the electrical conductivity was remarkably higher than that in the direction parallel to coating surface.
Titulo: Electron beam physical vapor deposition of YSZ electrolyte coatings for SOFCs

Sentencas: This mainly attributed to the typical columnar structure for EB-PVD coating and the existence of many grain boundaries along the direction parallel to coating surface.
Titulo: Electron beam physical vapor deposition of YSZ electrolyte coatings for SOFCs

Sentencas: For as-deposited coating, the gas permeability coefficient of 9.78 x 10 (5) cm(4) N (1) s (1) was obtained and this value was close to the critical value of YSZ electrolyte layer required for solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) operation.
Titulo: Electron beam physical vapor deposition of YSZ electrolyte coatings for SOFCs
